    dc:description "FIGURE 36. Collected specimens. Gerromorpha, Veliidae. A. Rhagovelia accedens, apterous male from Pimenta, Minas Gerais (−20.6003, −45.8150). B−D. Rhagovelia agra from Teresópolis, Rio de Janeiro (−22.4561, −42.996). B. Apterous male, dorsal view. C, D. Apterous female. C. Dorsal view. D. Lateral view. E. Rhagovelia aiuruoca, apterous male from São José do Barreiro, São Paulo (−22.7803, −44.6112). Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437924/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

